  "3047510": {
    "name": "Myths are 100% True",
    "steam_appid": 3047510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(A Game made by one of the %&amp;#@!*$ that worked on The Binding of Isaac: Repentance and Creator cult game 'At Least There is Čeda Čedović')</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Myths are 100% True </strong>is a Fast-Paced Combat Side-Scroller that feels like X-Files if it was made by 12 year olds in Windows Movie Maker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Play as Hlev Pekarovic -</strong> a newly hired ‘Photoslav’ and master of ‘Aggressive Photography’. He works for ‘Teorija Tortino’, one of the CEOs of ‘Big Myth Company’. Only with his skills can he create the world’s biggest documentation of myths and legends and make his newest internet video!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/dae65128edef094ec442b908f06a3d92.poster.avif?t=1764021147\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/dae65128edef094ec442b908f06a3d92.webm?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/dae65128edef094ec442b908f06a3d92.mp4?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Gameplay</strong> is an ideal synergy of Platforming and Combat. A Ridiculous movement system where dashing into slopes launches you in the air, yet somehow works hand in hand with the camera-based combat! (You can also buy infinite salad, but that's not as noteworthy)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/735f350031b89c8c63ae8e730e7b3af8.poster.avif?t=1764021147\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/735f350031b89c8c63ae8e730e7b3af8.webm?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/735f350031b89c8c63ae8e730e7b3af8.mp4?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game's theme</strong> is a mishmash of all sorts of stuff that interests us; grounded by bizarre themes such as 'Late 2000s GTA Myth videos', 'Early Y2K surreal Optimism' and 'Absurdist Comedy'.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/6c2f8a16fdcf277b6c79e45e4a19ac37.poster.avif?t=1764021147\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/6c2f8a16fdcf277b6c79e45e4a19ac37.webm?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047510/extras/6c2f8a16fdcf277b6c79e45e4a19ac37.mp4?t=1764021147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game’s tone</strong> is a throwback to the strange, yet more light-hearted and vibrant charm of the late 2000s internet. A Varied, Eccentric, Genuine, Replayable and Player-Expressive game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like the surreal feeling of seeing easter eggs and tiny details that are probably a reference to something highly specific and obscure but you cannot possibly guess what it is, then this game is for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
